3c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBuilding and maintaining the system (growing)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eScribbling on napkins or gesturing next to someone with a furrowed brow (conveying)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDocumentation which enumerates surface area or catalogs features may be exhaustive but often doesn't achieve either building or conveying the mental model of the subject in question. Using a well designed tool or product directly can achieve both.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhat are the tools and techniques which work for you? What makes them effective?\u003c/p\u003e\n","description_plain":"What are tools or techniques which well for conveying and growing mental model?\r\n\r\nTechniques I have seen which work well include:\r\n- Building and maintaining the system (growing)\r\n- Scribbling on napkins or gesturing next to someone with a furrowed brow (conveying)\r\n\r\nDocumentation which enumerates surface area or catalogs features may be exhaustive but often doesn't achieve either building or conveying the mental model of the subject in question. Using a well designed tool or product directly can achieve both.\r\n\r\nWhat are the tools and techniques which work for you? What makes them effective?","submitter_user":"mw","user_is_author":true,"tags":["ask","philosophy","programming"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/ubl3i2","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/ubl3i2/tools_techniques_for_conveying_mental"},{"short_id":"uswzil","created_at":"2026-07-02T08:31:04.000-05:00","title":"Opening up ‘Zero-Knowledge Proof’ technology to promote privacy in age assurance","url":"https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/technology/safety-security/opening-up-zero-knowledge-proof-technology-to-promote-privacy-in-age-assurance/","score":6,"flags":0,"comment_count":6,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"ndr","user_is_author":false,"tags":["privacy"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/uswzil","comments_url":"https://lobs